              {
                "desc": "A lightweight greatsword made of white iron with a silver sheen.</br>When swung rapidly, the flashes of light can blind the enemy.</br>However, this sword is not usually used as a weapon.</br>According to the way of warriors of old, when a comrade falls in battle, polished weapons will line the ground where they fell.</br>Though such rituals as these are no longer in fashion, some few still remember what they mean...</br>",
